description: Pick-Ups Plus, Inc. operates as a truck and SUV accessory retailer. It also offers dealership programs and franchise options. Pick-Ups Plus, Inc. was formerly known as Mr. Pickup and it changed its name to Pick-Ups Plus, Inc. in January 1994. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Mason, Ohio. It has store locations in Illinois, Kentucky, Ohio, and Texas.
